sequenceDiagram
  participant U as 用户
  participant H as Harness
  participant C as Capability Catalog
  participant M as Model
  participant S as Skill Runtime
  participant P as Tool Pipeline

  U->>H: 修复测试失败
  H->>C: 查询相关 skill 索引
  C-->>H: test-fix / code-review 摘要
  H->>M: 任务 + 轻量 SkillIndex + 最小工具
  M-->>H: intent: load_skill(test-fix)
  H->>S: 校验权限并渲染 Skill
  S-->>H: Skill 正文和运行边界
  H->>M: 注入 Skill 指南
  M-->>H: intent: Bash(npm test)
  H->>P: 统一执行管线
